 The 
\family typewriter
marsadm
\family default
 command checks that the disk device argument is really a block device,
 and that exclusive access to it is possible (as well as some further safety
 checks, e.g.
 matching sizes).
 However, MARS cannot know the 
\emph on
purpose
\emph default
