\series default
.
 This is a very desirable property: it ensures that nothing goes wrong when
 applying 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

too much
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 / starting your replay 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

too early
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

